Directories structure design:

welfare / --> Root base dir.
    CMakeLists.txt
    README
    configure
    doc/ --> Documetations.
        (Documentation generated by doxygen)
    test/ --> Unit tests.
        (Several unit tests.)
    tools/ --> The applications and tools.
        (Several tools directory and files)
    welfare/ --> Librarie codes.
        (Several library files)


